If you control an "X-Saber" Synchro Monster: Target 2 "X-Saber" monsters in your Graveyard; Special Summon both, ignoring their Summoning conditions, but their ATK become 0, also they are destroyed during this End Phase. You cannot conduct your Battle Phase the turn you activate this card. You can only activate 1 "Gottoms' Emergency Convocation" per turn.
